headline: Piper Sandler Boosts Price Target on Impinj (PI) to $140 Amid Sector Tailwinds
summary: Impinj Inc. (NASDAQ:PI) is one of the most oversold semiconductor stocks so far in 2025. On July 23, a Piper Sandler analyst raised his price target on Impinj (NASDAQ:PI) to $140 from $100, while reiterating his Overweight rating on the stock. The move follows earnings commentary from another company, Avery Dennison (NYSE:AVY), which the analyst views […]

headline: AVY Q2 Deep Dive: Trade Policy Pressures and High-Value Segment Growth Shape Outlook
summary: Adhesive manufacturing company Avery Dennison (NYSE:AVY) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales flat year on year at $2.22 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.42 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
